sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Stripe as Stripe Webhook
    participant Credit as Credit Orchestrator
    participant Ledger as Credit Transaction Service
    participant OutSys as OutSystems Credit API

    Stripe->>Credit: POST /credits/topup/webhook
    Credit->>Ledger: GET transaction by referenceId
    alt first delivery
        Ledger-->>Credit: not found
        Credit->>OutSys: PATCH new balance
        Credit->>Ledger: POST credit transaction with referenceId
        Credit-->>Stripe: 200 received
    else duplicate delivery
        Ledger-->>Credit: existing record found
        Credit-->>Stripe: 200 received without reapplying balance
    end
